{"tid":520293,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"時代力量鐵鍊鎖議場拒修《勞基法》　陳為廷：忍無可忍","createTime":"2018-01-05T09:19:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-05T10:41:32.000Z","uid":37554,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8f7f93e92023702a68a0817dd9a2eaf6c302fcf6","tid":520293,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T09:19:07.000Z","msg":"立法院今起召開臨時會，處理《勞動基準法》修法，鬆綁7休1，勞團下周起將夜宿立法院外抗議，時代力量今天也拿出鐵鍊，鎖住立法院議場大門，頗有當年太陽花學運氣勢。太陽花學運領袖、現任時代力量立院黨團助理陳為廷在臉書說，「忍無可忍！退無可退！」<br />\n <br />\n陳為廷說，民進黨今天強硬表決通過臨時會議程，下周將闖關《勞基法》三讀。時代力量5位委員剛剛已經佔領議場，用鎖鏈鎖住議場所有大門，行動會持續到下週，力阻《勞基法》闖關！訴求非常簡單：撤回《勞基法》修正案！<br />\n<br />\n陳為廷也說，時代力量呼籲及要求，請行政院以勞工權益為念，撤回《勞基法》修正案，聆聽勞工的聲音，踐行審慎的評估，給年輕的新世代，一個看得到的未來。（何哲欣／台北報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/eUePKKP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FeUePKKP.png&h=5cb5d6c7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"61a9e91ccfb8de87f7a12909095193a5a7295ad3","tid":520293,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T09:19:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://apisrc.edesk.stormmediagroup.com/s3/files/styles/smg-800x533-fp-wm/s3/media/image/2018/01/05/20180105-035202_U1841_M366410_d93b.jpg?itok=Qf9U45yJ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fapisrc.edesk.stormmediagroup.com%2Fs3%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Fsmg-800x533-fp-wm%2Fs3%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2018%2F01%2F05%2F20180105-035202_U1841_M366410_d93b.jpg%3Fitok%3DQf9U45yJ&h=70748ca3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d8a85580363647b446f6a967f91cbbbd63a9be5f","tid":520293,"uid":37554,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T09:21:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2018/01/05/realtime/4397824.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2018%2F01%2F05%2Frealtime%2F4397824.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050%26exp%3D3600&h=d2ffe363&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2018/01/05/realtime/4397822.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2018%2F01%2F05%2Frealtime%2F4397822.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050%26exp%3D3600&h=5f5b89ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2018/01/05/realtime/4397821.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2018%2F01%2F05%2Frealtime%2F4397821.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050%26exp%3D3600&h=1989bccf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"94887cb5784efb44622e59e5059b90d4f5f0b662","tid":520293,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T09:22:17.000Z","msg":"香港：打爆玻璃就係鬼"},{"pid":"718068f70ec46012e697e059e82d9067d8a68117","tid":520293,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T09:46:39.000Z","msg":"時力自鎖立院議場 綠委剪鎖突圍<br />\n<br />\n時代力量五名立委下午3時許突進入議場，並以鎖具自鎖於議場內，高掛「拒絕修惡的鎖鍊」，抗議「勞基法」修法。民進黨黨團立委聞訊，持油壓剪等器材，於下午4時50分許，分批剪斷各門口的鎖具，並進入議場，與時代力量黨團立委對峙中。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_2303578_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_2303578_1.jpg&h=afde6d0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xFsCJtNBrtU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DxFsCJtNBrtU&d=5eF4tT49bOmdx1L6XUUpv2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=e1580cc2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xFsCJtNBrtU</a>"},{"pid":"218361171b29c34ffab9869054e7b9fad21df460","tid":520293,"uid":69568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"94887cb5784efb44622e59e5059b90d4f5f0b662","tid":520293,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T09:22:17.000Z","msg":"香港：打爆玻璃就係鬼"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T09:56:08.000Z","msg":"仲好講嗰次，出師無名，誤信熱狗謠言"},{"pid":"8c2522d4b3fb509bc8bbc8481f51f967b555faec","tid":520293,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"218361171b29c34ffab9869054e7b9fad21df460","tid":520293,"uid":69568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"94887cb5784efb44622e59e5059b90d4f5f0b662","tid":520293,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T09:22:17.000Z","msg":"香港：打爆玻璃就係鬼"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T09:56:08.000Z","msg":"仲好講嗰次，出師無名，誤信熱狗謠言"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T10:41:12.000Z","msg":"不過泛民既反應真係無眼睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a82432c1e4d3a849fae51bdf4a68b85562ed79b0","tid":520293,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T10:41:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>香港：打爆玻璃就係鬼</blockquote>仲好講嗰次，出師無名，誤信熱狗謠言</blockquote>不過果次泛民既反應真係無眼睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"}]}